WEBVTT

00:01.010 --> 00:03.011
It's too much.

00:03.095 --> 00:06.093
It is a very generous gesture.

00:06.095 --> 00:08.093
Sir Henry has a son.

00:08.095 --> 00:09.733
Quite the golden-haired child.

00:09.735 --> 00:10.733
And?

00:10.735 --> 00:12.853
Perhaps they're
looking for the right girl.

00:12.855 --> 00:14.373
Anna?

00:14.375 --> 00:16.813
Do women really have such thoughts?

00:16.815 --> 00:17.855
Yes.

00:19.095 --> 00:21.653
Doesn't mean that we should do them.

00:21.655 --> 00:25.733
Before we got married,
I was in love with someone.

00:25.735 --> 00:27.173
Someone totally wrong.

00:27.175 --> 00:30.575
What could have made him love
someone who is so wrong for him?

00:31.735 --> 00:33.575
I need to see who she is.

00:34.815 --> 00:37.813
That woman made a promise to James,
and to me!

00:37.815 --> 00:38.933
She saved his life.

00:38.935 --> 00:40.493
And now she threatens to ruin it.

00:40.495 --> 00:41.815
My husband was Jewish.

00:43.175 --> 00:44.655
Rene died...

00:46.935 --> 00:48.135
in Dachau.

